    "description":  "Assessment tool to review potential options for installing Combined Heat and Power (CHP) for a given site.",
    "details":  {
                    "attachments":  [

                                    ],
                    "body":  "\u003cdiv class=\"govspeak\"\u003e\u003ch2 id=\"the-chp-site-assessment-tool\"\u003eThe \u003cabbr title=\"Combined Heat and Power\"\u003eCHP\u003c/abbr\u003e Site Assessment Tool\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis application is a free tool allowing users to get an indicative assessment and review potential options for installing Combined Heat and Power (\u003cabbr title=\"Combined Heat and Power\"\u003eCHP\u003c/abbr\u003e) on a particular site. It has been carefully designed for users who have limited knowledge of \u003cabbr title=\"Combined Heat and Power\"\u003eCHP\u003c/abbr\u003e. It guides a user through the information required to carry out an indicative assessment showing whether a particular site warrants further investigation into \u003cabbr title=\"Combined Heat and Power\"\u003eCHP\u003c/abbr\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe \u003cabbr title=\"Combined Heat and Power\"\u003eCHP\u003c/abbr\u003e Site Assessment Tool has been designed to be simple and intuitive. For a given site it provides the 5 best options showing their:\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003e\n\u003cabbr title=\"Combined Heat and Power\"\u003eCHP\u003c/abbr\u003e capacity\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003ecapital cost\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003epayback period\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003enet present value\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003ecost savings, and\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eprimary energy savings\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eYou need to register to use the Site Assessment Tool. This is necessary to allow you to save and compare several scenarios.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch3 id=\"features\"\u003eFeatures\u003c/h3\u003e\n\n\u003ctable\u003e\n  \u003ctbody\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eFeatures\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eVisitor\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eRegistered User\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eWizard based format (to reduce confusion)\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eYes\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eYes\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eData upload direct to site\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eYes\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eYes\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eFlexible tool navigation\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eYes\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eYes\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eStep specific help\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eYes\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eYes\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eScenario save\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eNo\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eYes\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n    \u003ctr\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eMultiple scenarios\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eNo\u003c/td\u003e\n      \u003ctd\u003eYes\u003c/td\u003e\n    \u003c/tr\u003e\n  \u003c/tbody\u003e\n\u003c/table\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"use-the-tool\"\u003eUse the Tool\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"call-to-action\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca rel=\"external\" href=\"http://chptools.decc.gov.uk/CHPAssessment/(S(q2haqbi5u42qav2w12rlothj))/default.aspx\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003eCHP Site Assessment Tool\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003c/div\u003e",
